






#lg A	sa-gida


@(A.1 = 1-13) The great house is as great as a mountain. The house of @wDN{Enlil} is as great as a mountain. The house of @wDN{Ninlil} is as great as a mountain. The bedchamber is as great as a mountain. The house which knows no daylight is as great as a mountain. The house at the Lofty Gate is as great as a mountain. The house at the Gate of Well-being is as great as a mountain. The courtyard of @wDN{Enlil} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Ḫursaŋ-galama} is as great as a mountain. The holy Renowned Gate is as great as a mountain. The Gate from which Grain is never Diverted is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Ubšu-unkena} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Ŋa-ŋiš-šua} is as great as a mountain.

@(A.14 = 14-27) The house of @wDN{Ninlil} is as great as a mountain. The gate Kan-innamra is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{E-itida-buru} is as great as a mountain. The courtyard of the @wTN{Egal-maḫ} is as great as a mountain. The lofty @wTN{E-itida-buru} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Entum-galzu} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Innam-gidazu} is as great as a mountain. The @wDN{Suen} Gate is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Du-kug}, the holy place, is as great as a mountain. The field of @wTN{E-dima} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{@wDN{Ane}-ŋara} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Ašte}, the pure place, is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{E-tilla-maḫ} is as great as a mountain. The @wTN{Ŋa-apina} is as great as a mountain.

#trailer rubric	sa-gida


@(A.28 = 28) @fsux{Sa-gida}.

#lg B	jicgijal


