#lg C	kirugu


@(C.31 = 31-41) For him who declares it, for him who declares it, the house comes forth like the daylight. For him who declares that he is of the mountain, the house comes forth like the daylight. For him who declares that he is of the house of @wDN{Enlil}, the house comes forth like the daylight. For him who declares that he is of the house of @wDN{Ninlil}, the house comes forth like the daylight. For him who declares that he is of the house of @wDN{Ninurta}, the house comes forth like the daylight, for him who declares that he is of the house of the princely son.

#trailer rubric	kirugu


@(C.42 = 42) @fsux{Kirugu}.

#lg D	sa-jara


@(D.43 = 43-52) The house towers high in full grandeur; in its midst is a mountain of aromatic cedars. The house of @wDN{Enlil} towers high in full grandeur; in its midst is a mountain of aromatic cedars. The house of @wDN{Ninlil} towers high in full grandeur; in its midst is a mountain of aromatic cedars. The courtyard of @wDN{Enlil} towers high in full grandeur; in its midst is a mountain of aromatic cedars. The courtyard of @wDN{Ninlil} towers high in full grandeur; in its midst is a mountain of aromatic cedars.

#trailer rubric	sa-jara


@(D.53 = 53) @fsux{Sa-ŋara}.

