#lg F	unknown


@(F.56 = 56-68) Its king is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. The hero @wDN{Ninurta} is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. The offspring (?) of @wDN{Ninlil} is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. The lord, the hero (?) of the @wTN{E-kur}, is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. The offspring (?) of @wDN{Enlil} is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. Lord @wDN{Ašimbabbar} is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth. The princely son of the @wTN{E-kur} is worthy of @wDN{Enlil} the king in the true house of youth.

